snippet.title: Reknum Fantasy of Dreams - The voices behind it trailer
snippet.description:
New #Reknum Fantasy of Dreams trailer focused on voiceover for the game!

Let's welcome:

🟣 Aimee Smith
🟣 Nola Klop
🟣 Nathalie Ferare
🟣 David Ko

They have done an outstanding job bringing the game to life with their artistic voiceover!

Now in development for #NintendoSwitch & #PS4
